    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_4_6688-6874",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6688-6874",
      "markText": "实际上蒋介石与张学良的不抵抗有明显的区别：蒋介石欲避免全国抗战而不抵抗，张学良因主张全面抗战而不抵抗；蒋介石可用局部抵抗来避免或拖延全国抗战，张学良却不愿独自局部抗战，只能用不抵抗等待全国抗战。[12]",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6688&rangeEnd=6874",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6688&rangeEnd=6874"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_43_1014-1156",
      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "1014-1156",
      "markText": "如冯玉祥称：“不抗日不是卖国贼是什么呢？如说抗日有多年准备，岂不知水涨船高，你预备人家也预备，你长五倍人家高五十倍呢。”[18",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=43&rangeStart=1014&rangeEnd=1156",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=43&rangeStart=1014&rangeEnd=1156"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_6_3220-3295",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3220-3295",
      "markText": "具体而言，本书的“地方实力派”一词，其内涵主要包括两个方面：一是具有一定的实力，或掌握一定军队，或军队与地盘兼而有之；二是与中央政府保持一定的独立性。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3220&rangeEnd=3295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3220&rangeEnd=3295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_15_5458-5519",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "5458-5519",
      "markText": "对蒋介石而言，改编后的西北军各部驻扎北方各地，仍是潜在威胁，以“剿共”之名将西北军分调南方各省遂成为其合乎逻辑的策略选择。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=5458&rangeEnd=5519",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=5458&rangeEnd=5519"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_45_4042-4133",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "4042-4133",
      "markText": "蒋介石在名分上的韬光养晦，有所为有所不为，是以退为进的策略之需，只待时机成熟，必然追求绝对的不受支配的权力以及与之相匹配的名位。蒋介石对地方实力派的绥靖与妥协亦是依托不断强大的武力，",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=4042&rangeEnd=4133",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=4042&rangeEnd=4133"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_21_2271-2299",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2271-2299",
      "markText": "原桂系巨头之一黄绍竑可能是最早建言蒋介石优先解决两广的。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2271&rangeEnd=2299",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2271&rangeEnd=2299"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_22_4964-5031",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "4964-5031",
      "markText": "石达开在江西、湖北等地数次挫败蒋介石非常推崇的曾国藩，却又惨败于四川。这样深刻的历史教训，可能也使蒋介石在派中央军入川问题上谨慎从事。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=4964&rangeEnd=5031",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=4964&rangeEnd=5031"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_26_640-684",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "640-684",
      "markText": "1927年第一次国共合作分裂后，“剿共”几乎成为国民政府话语体系中与抗日同等的政治正确。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=640&rangeEnd=684",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=640&rangeEnd=684"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_42_8401-8469",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "8401-8469",
      "markText": "吾料倭俄正式宣战，不能出于本年六月之内。”“俄蒙协定宣布之日实即倭俄战局完成之时，俄寇狡诈疑忌与倭寇狭隘横暴，决不能长以隐忍而不破裂也。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=8401&rangeEnd=8469",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=8401&rangeEnd=8469"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_8_2751-2821",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2751-2821",
      "markText": "蒋介石的这些自我记录或主要是凸显自己在错综复杂的政治环境中毅然坚挺的种种不易，但如此频繁的记录恰恰也是一个政治新手进入政治中枢后的真实反映。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2751&rangeEnd=2821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2751&rangeEnd=2821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37567150_19_4902-5045",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "4902-5045",
      "markText": "蒋纬国口中的战略是指南京中央势力“随着共军进入云贵川，使中国达成真正的统一”。“以当时的情况来说，这是一个非常成功的政治战略。”",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37567150&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=4902&rangeEnd=5045",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eaf32570723d3aaeeaf775d?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=4902&rangeEnd=5045"
